item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

Ping basically means to connect to the server and see how strong a connection you get. It makes a socket, connects the socket to the server, and then takes a measurement of how long it took to do. Less time it took, better connection you’ll get.
